### RAG 同步查询
POST http://localhost:8000/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "程波有机器学习的经验吗？",
  "search_params": {
    "top_k": 5,
    "response_mode": "compact"
  }
}

### RAG 流式查询（SSE）
POST http://localhost:8000/api/query/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "狮民肋板水池有什么问题",
  "search_params": {
    "top_k": 5,
    "response_mode": "compact"
  }
}

